Old README
==========

Build cairo debs with --enable-gl 


Build everything
$ ./build.sh

Run tests from cairo-gl-smoke-tests
$ ./masking-filling-stroking-glx
$ ./operators-glx

Run bash to have a look around
$ ./run.sh
